	<ul>
		<li>Your operating system and version (e.g. Windows XP, OS X 10.5)</li>
		<li>The browser and version you are using (e.g. Internet Explorer 7, Firefox 3, Safari 3.1)</li>
	</ul>
</p>
<p>
